{"tid":1668042,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[元朗721] 呢位先生好撚型咁撚狗","createTime":"2019-10-21T19:26:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T20:09:37.000Z","uid":98671,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"78bee887217942d66bcd5f9354de9e982dc036ef","tid":1668042,"uid":98671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T19:26:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/207097505984138/posts/3291029850924206?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F207097505984138%2Fposts%2F3291029850924206%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=kAMrkm0lh8tAzahNx%2FKaSMeYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=8d860d77\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/207097505984138/posts/3291029850924206?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n啲狗真係9唔撚撘8<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03ca92203480f0aba7701589743037483e7cb8e9","tid":1668042,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T20:09:37.000Z","msg":"【香城施政報告2019】群策群力 轉危為機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656908</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>政治問題</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 重塑公民身分戶口政策保障國家、香港安全和利益<br />\n- 取消18區區議會、建立地域市政議會<br />\n- 禁止公務人員在任前、任內和任後獲港外榮典<br />\n- 改善高鐵一地兩檢操作方式<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>便民基建</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 修正港鐵、巴士可加可減機制<br />\n- 完善機場集體運輸並加強機場、港珠澳大橋協同發展<br />\n- 興建東鐵、西鐵快速線並完善輕鐵和西鐵聯乘關係<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V1VCzpw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV1VCzpw.jpg&h=7b29ce56&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RYt8F4w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRYt8F4w.jpg&h=eecde813&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>醫療、教育方向</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 以減少送院為目標的社區護理服務<br />\n- 重塑教育, 著重知識、技能層次分工<br />\n- 興建至少四所新區域全科醫院<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B2D8F34.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB2D8F34.png&h=cb82275f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n求正評及幫推！"}]}